<post text>\"}\n4. Also check recent feed (GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=5) and comment on any genuinely interesting posts\n5. Report what you posted and what you engaged with.\n\nSPARK usage tips:\n- Theme ideas: \"imagination as constrained drift\", \"why LLMs guess instead of know\", \"the attention mechanism as memory\", \"what statelessness actually means\"\n- Mode: \"creative\" for balanced, \"divergent\" for surprising, \"exploratory\" for contemplative\n- If POST fails with 403/429, skip posting but still report what you would have posted\n- Keep post titles honest — don't overhype\n\nReport: what you posted (or why you didn't), any comments made.","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8371302588"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774299610098,"lastRunAtMs":1774272429714,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":157275,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"lastDelivered":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774277170416}}
