{"type":"message","id":"22148b77","parentId":"b9464294","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:08:14.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API scaffolding exists. Let me check the main.py and the routes/creative.py to understand what we have.","thinkingSignature":"51f77d14667bb2270e7850834273b3b3f5e7d9f44433316ad37e7a5f10e59c6f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_natnma0dds7f_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\api\\main.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_natnma0dds7f_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\api\\routes\\creative.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":46279,"output":106,"cacheRead":13610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774278490482}}
{"type":"message","id":"f52c45ef","parentId":"22148b77","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:08:14.530Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_natnma0dds7f_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nSPARK API Server\nRun: python -m uvicorn spark.api.main:app --reload --port 8765\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# Ensure spark core is importable\nSPARK_DIR = Path(__file__).parent.parent\nsys.path.insert(0, str(SPARK_DIR))\nsys.path.insert(0, str(SPARK_DIR.parent))\n\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\nfrom fastapi.middleware.cors import CORSMiddleware\n\nfrom spark.api.routes.creative import router as creative_router\n\napp = FastAPI(\n    title=\"SPARK — Creative Intelligence API\",\n    description=\"Semantic Pattern Recognition via Associative Drift + Constrained Steering\",\n    version=\"0.1.0\",\n)\n\n# CORS — allow all for dev\napp.add_middleware(\n    CORSMiddleware,\n    allow_origins=[\"*\"],\n    allow_credentials=True,\n    allow_methods=[\"*\"],\n    allow_headers=[\"*\"],\n)\n\napp.include_router(creative_router)\n\n\n@app.get(\"/health\")\nasync def health():\n    return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"spark\"}\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    import uvicorn\n    uvicorn.run(\"spark.api.main:app\", host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8765, reload=True)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774278494500}}
{"type":"message","id":"9671ac17","parentId":"f52c45ef","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:08:14.566Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_natnma0dds7f_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"SPARK Creative Writing API — /v1/spark/generate\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional, List\n\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, HTTPException\nfrom pydantic import BaseModel\n\n# Add spark core to path\nSPARK_DIR = Path(__file__).parent.parent.parent  # .../spark/\nsys.path.insert(0, str(SPARK_DIR))\nsys.path.insert(0, str(SPARK_DIR.parent))\n\nfrom spark.core.llm_mapper import CreativeMapper\nfrom spark.demo import build_thematic_graph, run_drift\n\nrouter = APIRouter()\n\n\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Request / Response models\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nclass GenerateRequest(BaseModel):\n    theme: str = \"love in the age of AI\"\n    domain: str = \"all\"\n    mode: str = \"creative\"  # creative | divergent | exploratory\n    steering: float = 0.3\n    n: int = 3\n    steps: int = 30\n    seed_moment: Optional[str] = None\n    constraints: Optional[List[str]] = None\n    ollama_url: Optional[str] = None\n    model: Optional[str] = None\n\n\nclass Variation(BaseModel):\n    id: str\n    text: str\n    concepts: List[str]\n    coherence_score: float\n    entropy: float\n    regime: str\n\n\nclass GenerateResponse(BaseModel):\n    variations: List[Variation]\n    meta: dict\n\n\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Helpers\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n\ndef _detect_provider(ollama_url: Optional[str] = None) -> tuple:\n    \"\"\"Detect best available provider and URL.\"\"\"\n    if ollama_url:\n        return \"ollama\", ollama_url\n    if os.environ.get(\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"):\n        return \"openai\", None\n    if os.environ.get(\"ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\"):\n        return \"anthropic\", None\n    if ollama_url := os.environ.get(\"OLLAMA_URL\"):\n        return \"ollama\", ollama_url\n    # Fallback: try localhost\n    return \"ollama\", \"http://localhost:11434\"\n\n\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n# Routes\n# -------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n@router.post(\"/v1/spark/generate\", response_model=GenerateResponse)\nasync def generate(req: GenerateRequest):\n    \"\"\"\n    Generate creative text via SPARK's drift chamber.\n\n    The drift chamber activates concepts through semantic diffusion\n    guided by steering toward the theme. Activated concepts are then\n    mapped to prose by an LLM.\n    \"\"\"\n    # 1. Build thematic graph\n    try:\n        graph, concept_to_cluster, goal_concepts, all_concepts = build_thematic_graph(req.domain)\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=f\"Graph build failed: {e}\")\n\n    # 2. Run drift\n    try:\n        graph, history = run_drift(\n            graph=graph,\n            concept_to_cluster=concept_to_cluster,\n            goal_concepts=goal_concepts,\n            steering=req.steering,\n            steps=req.steps,\n        )\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=f\"Drift run failed: {e}\")\n\n    # 3. Extract top concepts\n    sorted_nodes = sorted(graph.nodes.values(), key=lambda n: n.activation, reverse=True)\n    top_nodes = sorted_nodes[:20]\n    concept_activations = {n.id: n.activation for n in top_nodes if n.activation > 0.05}\n\n    # 4. Map to text via LLM\n    provider, provider_url = _detect_provider(req.ollama_url)\n    model = req.model or (\"qwen2.5:7b\" if provider == \"ollama\" else None)\n\n    try:\n        mapper = CreativeMapper(provider=provider, model=model)\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=f\"Mapper init failed: {e}\")\n\n    # Patch Ollama URL if using remote\n    if provider == \"ollama\" and provider_url and provider_url != \"http://localhost:11434\":\n        import requests as _req\n        _original_post = _req.post\n        def _patched_post(url, json, timeout, **kwargs):\n            return _original_post(f\"{provider_url}/api/generate\", json=json, timeout=timeout)\n        _req.post = _patched_post\n\n    try:\n        results = mapper.map_concepts_to_text(\n            concept_activations=concept_activations,\n            theme=req.theme,\n            mode=req.mode,\n            n_variations=req.n,\n            seed_moment=req.seed_moment,\n            user_constraints=req.constraints,\n        )\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=f\"Text generation failed: {e}\")\n    finally:\n        if provider == \"ollama\" and provider_url and provider_url != \"http://localhost:11434\":\n            _req.post = _original_post\n\n    # 5. Build response\n    strong_count = len(graph.get_strong_nodes(0.3))\n    # Import activation_entropy from drift_chamber (used by demo.py)\n    sys.path.insert(0, str(SPARK_DIR.parent / \"drift-chamber\"))\n    from drift_chamber.metrics import activation_entropy\n    entropy = activation_entropy(graph)\n\n    variations = [\n        Variation(\n            id=r[\"id\"],\n            text=r[\"text\"],\n            concepts=r[\"concepts\"],\n            coherence_score=strong_count / max(len(graph.nodes), 1),\n            entropy=entropy,\n            regime=\"IMAGINATIVE\" if strong_count > 5 else \"EXPLORING\",\n        )\n        for r in results\n    ]\n\n    return GenerateResponse(\n        variations=variations,\n        meta={\n            \"domain\": req.domain,\n            \"mode\": req.mode,\n            \"steering\": req.steering,\n            \"steps\": req.steps,\n            \"provider\": provider,\n            \"n_concepts\": len(graph.nodes),\n            \"strong_concepts\": strong_count,\n            \"entropy\": round(entropy, 3),\n            \"regime\": \"IMAGINATIVE\" if strong_count > 5 else \"EXPLORING\",\n        },\n    )\n\n\n@router.get(\"/v1/spark/domains\")\nasync def list_domains():\n    \"\"\"List available domain configs.\"\"\"\n    return {\n        \"domains\": [\n            {\"id\": \"all\", \"description\": \"All creative concepts\"},\n            {\"id\": \"romance\", \"description\": \"Love, longing, connection, loss\"},\n            {\"id\": \"scifi\", \"description\": \"Technology, cosmos, humanity, creation\"},\n            {\"id\": \"thriller\", \"description\": \"Tension, power, pursuit, secrets\"},\n            {\"id\": \"literary\", \"description\": \"Craft, meaning, form, expression\"},\n            {\"id\": \"horror\", \"description\": \"Death, dread, flesh, threshold\"},\n            {\"id\": \"poetry\", \"description\": \"Sensory, image, rhythm, metaphor\"},\n        ],\n        \"modes\": [\"creative\", \"divergent\", \"exploratory\"],\n    }\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774278494530}}
{"type":"message","id":"851c504f","parentId":"9671ac17","timestamp":"2026-03-23T15:08:25.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - the API scaffolding is there but there's a problem: `spark.api.routes.creative` imports from `spark.demo` which doesn't exist in this form. The `creative.py` imports `from spark.demo import build_thematic_graph, run_drift` - but the actual demo is `demo.py` at the root of the spark project, and the functions might not be named that way.\n\nLet me check what's actually exported from demo.py and the drift_chamber:","thinkingSignature":"38825f01092e70eca4e6bb52da9c12449f1851623be7a0411d635d36fb118e0d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i8sor3pnxcs7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Select-String -Path C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\spark\\demo.py -Pattern 'def build_thematic_graph|def run_drift|def drift_cycle' 2>$null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48182,"output":163,"cacheRead":13610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61955,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774278494567}}
